CITY DIME SAVINGS & LOAN ASS’N, Respondent, v. LOBDELL et al., Appellants (two cases). (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. March 27, 1894.) Action by the City Dime Savings & Loan Association against William A. Lobdell and others.

Argued before DWIGHT, P. J., and LEWIS, HAIGHT, and BRADLEY, JJ.

No opinion.' Appeal dismissed, unless printed papers are served on or before the second Tuesday of the term.
